milestones.description: This is the highest match aggregate (467) involving teams South Africa & West Indies in ODIs
Wessels has broken the record for most catches in an innings (4) in ODIs for SA, going past Jonty Rhodes's 2
Allan Donald has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (13) for SA, going past Adrian Kuiper
